Package: MicrobialCommunityDistribution
Title: Distribute different type of microbial cells on a 2D plane
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Xavier", "Raynaud", , "xavier.raynaud@sorbonne-universite.fr", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9065-2867"))
Description: This package can be used to create spatial communities of microbial cells in a 2D space. Three categories of cells are available (isolated, round colonies and filamentous colonies), and cells can have phylum information. 
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
